               <msContents>
                  <summary>Seven Printed Booklets, bound as
                    One Book: Book One, Sa’atat, Miracles of Mary, Miracles of Jesus, and other miracles,
                    Book Two, Sanie Golgota,
                    Book Three, Malke Ragu’el,
                    Book Four, Malke Ragu’el,
                    Book Five, Homilies of Ragu’el, Homiles of Fanu’el, Image of Ragu’el, and Image of Fanu’el,
                    Book Six, Explanations of Jesus,
                    Book Seven, Sword of the Trinity, Säyfä Śǝllase, and Image of the Trinity</summary>
